X-WR-CALNAME:Weaver line disruption
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-07T03:30:00&endDate=2026-06-07T09:15:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Sunday 7 June\, until 1015\, no service between Liverpool Street and Cheshunt / Chingford / Enfield Town. Please use London Underground and London Buses connections between Liverpool Street and Hackney Downs / Seven Sisters. GREATER ANGLIA and STANSTED EXPRESS trains will not call at Hackney Downs or Seven Sisters. Replacement buses operate.
DTEND:20260607T091500Z
DTSTART:20260607T033000Z
SUMMARY:Weaver line: Planned Closure
UID:56b91c8a-1aa0-4006-875f-3f732e1aab01@56b9.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-11T21:45:00&endDate=2026-06-12T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Monday 8\, Tuesday 9\, Wednesday 10 and Thursday 11 June\, after 2245 each evening\, no service between Hackney Downs and Cheshunt / Enfield Town. Use London Underground connections between Central London and Seven Sisters\, and for Rectory Road and Stoke Newington\, use Clapton station. Last trains operate at 2243 from Liverpool Street to Cheshunt (except on Wednesday when it is at 2213)\, 2250 from Enfield Town to Liverpool Street\, 2258 from Liverpool Street to Enfield Town and 2259 from Cheshunt to Liverpool Street. Replacement buses operate.
